{"tid":590023,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PC/Mac] 電腦版暴龍機 DVPet","createTime":"2018-03-12T09:19:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T20:31:14.000Z","uid":14404,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"598534566bf847c7ce92c1c6414bc9aedf7bd3db","tid":590023,"uid":14404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T09:19:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zc5SiQV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fzc5SiQV.png&h=dabf4227&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最近無端端起癮想玩下暴龍機<br />\n咁啱發現有鬼佬整咗隻新嘅暴龍機java game for電腦玩<br />\n睇佢個log最近仲有keep住update<br />\n好似話有ver.1-6 超過400隻數碼暴龍<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ahvPa1J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FahvPa1J.png&h=ae431c30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n時間可以跟現實速度(之後可以任改時間)或者去到6倍速(6倍速冇得改時間但係有暫停功能)<br />\n同埋最重要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有得SAVE</span></span><br />\n所以唔使24hr mon住，得閒load返save就ok<br />\n(load要自己打返個save名所以一開始改名是但改個易記就得，唔記得都可以開game file睇返)<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/WtUWjd1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FWtUWjd1.png&h=a4616290&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(一開始改時間，1箭咀正常速度，3箭咀6倍速)<br />\n同埋好似可以連機對打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原post:<a href=\"https://withthewill.net/threads/18418-Digimon-V-Pet-fangame-for-PC-(alpha)\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwiththewill.net%2Fthreads%2F18418-Digimon-V-Pet-fangame-for-PC-%28alpha%29&d=x9LhHYmcYY%2BSM2472jRuA6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=7cca53e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://withthewill.net/threads/18418-Digimon-V-Pet-fangame-for-PC-(alpha)</a> <br />\nDL link :<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Wag4q1XC1xm2bpiVM9DxwsAeU8h7EIh6/view\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1Wag4q1XC1xm2bpiVM9DxwsAeU8h7EIh6%2Fview&d=x9LhHYmcYY%2BSM2472jRuA6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=300b0eef\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Wag4q1XC1xm2bpiVM9DxwsAeU8h7EIh6/view</a><br />\n如果想一路做野一路睇住佢嘅話可以試下用DeskPins將隻game置頂<br />\nDeskPins(解壓即用) : <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/15sS5B12xIb-JjHjZshZ4m0R_HE_6wJEP/view\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F15sS5B12xIb-JjHjZshZ4m0R_HE_6wJEP%2Fview&d=x9LhHYmcYY%2BSM2472jRuA6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=3823bd9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/15sS5B12xIb-JjHjZshZ4m0R_HE_6wJEP/view</a>"},{"pid":"c3fd542383c7443ac8881248a2fc07e9a24f7c64","tid":590023,"uid":14404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T09:50:29.000Z","msg":"我都係啱啱先開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99ebf52032268ffd1d045d4806274743d4368b86","tid":590023,"uid":14404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T10:09:41.000Z","msg":"睇錯咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3箭咀係 現實6秒 = game1分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd070e6e972f44c9524f0adef945a93795093603","tid":590023,"uid":22221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T11:14:30.000Z","msg":"有冇手機版"},{"pid":"353e713ded0598c2b7e47e3e873f6f56b86a635f","tid":590023,"uid":14404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd070e6e972f44c9524f0adef945a93795093603","tid":590023,"uid":22221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T11:14:30.000Z","msg":"有冇手機版"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T11:29:19.000Z","msg":"手機版其他人有整<br />\n上google play/app store search vpet應該有<br />\n不過冇暫停冇save冇得改時間<br />\n除非真係好得閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75f1015a4d32402464cf3780e95d908e80d9b8e4","tid":590023,"uid":10284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T12:34:38.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"f6fe838ebe0bf3c80